{
  "stem": "521.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A Desiderio.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which is nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe a John.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Instead of an Oscar I'm going to get a John.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I certainly I'm going to get the--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm just joking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm going to get the John, anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, before we got to Mauthausen, we went from Eisenerz up the mountain, and then we went down the mountain.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As we went down the mountain, the Germans started to shoot us, aimlessly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now some people were shot and he fell, and then the next fellow who went after it, maybe tripped or maybe stepped on it, or maybe could walk over it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now the people who were on the ground because they were shot-- there were quite a few, I guess it was about over 100-- the other people who were stumbling into it, they had fallen and since the rest of the people were intimidated by the shooting, they were trampling over it.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there were many people who have been trampled to death by the thousands of Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So not only the really hit people have died but also the ones who were stumbling.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, it went on for about-- I would say about 15, 20 minutes and then some German officers in one staff car, is whatever, arrived and then the shootings have stopped.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK, now we went to a place called Steyr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a small city, and as we walked through the main square, there was a young woman with a baby, a young kid in the carriage.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was dropping a bun in front of us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I picked it up and was saving it with my friend, Suge, and then we split it in half.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
